4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes weekly, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will build foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. It emphasizes risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Courses are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop